query:
ALTER TABLE distributors 
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS firstName VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS lastName VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS phone VARCHAR(50),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS address TEXT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS city VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS state VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS zipCode VARCHAR(20),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS dateOfBirth VARCHAR(20),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS ssnLast4 VARCHAR(4),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS taxId VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS taxIdType ENUM('ssn', 'ein'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS businessEntityType ENUM('individual', 'llc', 'corporation', 'partnership'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS businessName VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS businessEin VARCHAR(50),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS businessAddress TEXT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS businessCity VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS businessState VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS businessZipCode VARCHAR(20),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS emergencyContactName VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS emergencyContactPhone VARCHAR(50),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS emergencyContactRelationship VARCHAR(100),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS bankName VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS bankAccountType ENUM('checking', 'savings'),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS bankAccountLast4 VARCHAR(4),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS bankRoutingNumber VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS bankAccountNumber VARCHAR(255),
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS enrollmentPackageId INT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS autoshipEnabled BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE NOT NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS autoshipPackageId INT,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS nextAutoshipDate TIMESTAMP,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS taxInfoCompleted BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE NOT NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS taxInfoCompletedAt TIMESTAMP,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS agreedToPoliciesAt TIMESTAMP,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS agreedToTermsAt TIMESTAMP,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS w9Submitted BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE NOT NULL,
ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS w9SubmittedAt TIMESTAMP;
